column2: tahil_v1 <- separate(data = tahil_raw, col = grain_type, into = c("main_type", "product_type"), sep = " ve ")

tahil <- separate(tahil, product_type, into = c("product_code", "product_name"), sep = "^\\S*\\K\\s+")
